    "This finding reflects the increasing investment in the development of innovative technologies to improve language education and highlights the importance of continued research and development in this area to advance the field of language education.",
    "It is evident in the literature that RALL is a rapidly developing field, and there is increasing attention to the use of robots for language teaching and learning (Khalifa et al., 2019).",
